Project 4 - Visualization

Overview

This visualization shows a wordcloud of the most significant positive/negative terms. Negative terms are stacked at top, and positive terms at bottom. The size of terms in the wordcloud are relative to number of reviews they have appeared in. Other key aspects include:

  • These terms come from our custom vocabulary - previously used in the sentiment anaysis classification model.
  • Custom vocabulary terms are further restricted in an attempt to make this visualization more meaningful. The additional mods include:
    • Some additional stopwords removed
    • Terms are limited to bigrams only
